{
  "text": "Shift from \ue061-to \ue062-MHC in PTU-treated rat hearts PTU treatment has been shown to induce a shift from \ue061-to \ue062-MHC isoform, without any significant changes in the expression of other myofilament proteins [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . PTU-induced hypothyroidism silences the \ue061-MHC promoter and activates the \ue062-MHC promoter, resulting in the myocardial expression of \ue062-MHC [CITATION_4] . As shown in Fig. 2 A, PTU treatment of rats induced a nearcomplete shift to \ue062-MHC isoform in the left ventricles.",
  "correct_citation": {
